      "description": "- Resolved all Obsidian plugin linter issues (no static styles, no unsupported API, no onunload detach).\r\n- Replaced eval/new Function with a custom safe math evaluator.\r\n- Replaced global document references with activeDocument for full popout window compatibility.\r\n- Added \"Chart Color Theme\" option in settings (Classic, Pastel, Neon, Monochrome).\r\n- Replaced native setting theme selectors with custom modern dropdowns.\r\n- Implemented lazy loading in drilldown panels using IntersectionObserver.\r\n- Added Radar chart support.\r\n",
